                    The goal of this program is to train students in strategic information management and knowledge management in businesses and various
                    organizations.                    
                </p>

                <h3 class="smaller_heading"> II.2.2. Specific goals </h3>
                <p class="description"> 
                    <strong> Common run with the mention </strong><br/>
                    This program allows the student to:<br/>
                </p>
                <ul class="one_list">
                    <li> Understand information needs and translate these needs into a built-in approach, </li>
                    <li> Collect and process information in a relevant way, </li>
                    <li> Know how to identify misinformation and react to rumors,</li>
                    <li> Address information security issues. </li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="small_heading"> II.3. Program approach </h3>
                <p class="description"> 
                    The program prepares for a specialized course in Business Intelligence for companies or public administration.
                </p>

